<p>
 A sheet of exercises is a gathering of exercises on a given subject. It
 reflects a certain teaching goal, and can be used in an environment of virtual
 classes for the purpose of control students' progress.
</p>
<p>
 This database contains a collection of publically accessible exercise sheets.
 You can freely test your knowledge on any of them, or if you are the
 supervisor of a virtual class, insert some of them into your class.
</p>